76
00:04:04,476 --> 00:04:05,756
As for the second option...

77
00:04:17,556 --> 00:04:18,316
Everyone shared their dreams.

78
00:04:18,316 --> 00:04:19,146
What about you?

79
00:04:19,146 --> 00:04:20,146
What do you wish to do in the future?

80
00:04:20,436 --> 00:04:21,116
Me?

81
00:04:22,996 --> 00:04:24,586
