165
00:08:29,516 --> 00:08:32,106
(That is me, Huang Yingzi.)

166
00:08:32,706 --> 00:08:33,506
(My father said)

167
00:08:33,506 --> 00:08:35,276
(we're the descendants
of Huang Feihong.)

168
00:08:35,436 --> 00:08:38,276
(Therefore, helping the weak
and upholding justice are my duties.)

169
00:08:38,586 --> 00:08:41,076
(My dream is
to rid the world of injustice.)

170
00:08:41,706 --> 00:08:42,586
(Sometimes,)

171
00:08:42,586 --> 00:08:44,226
(I would drag the other guys)

172
00:08:44,226 --> 00:08:45,556
