173
00:08:46,226 --> 00:08:49,156
(For example, this ridiculous play.)

174
00:08:52,196 --> 00:08:54,826
(Although the audience has no idea
what the plot is all about,)

175
00:08:55,226 --> 00:08:56,556
(all six of us know)

176
00:08:57,036 --> 00:08:57,866
(that this tale)

177
00:08:58,156 --> 00:09:00,706
(started from the night
we first met each other.)

178
00:09:01,226 --> 00:09:02,746
(Since that night,)

179
00:09:03,436 --> 00:09:05,626
(all of us became an important part)

180
00:09:06,036 --> 00:09:07,626
(in each other's lives.)

181
00:09:22,076 --> 00:09:24,676
Is there a monster?

182
00:09:25,746 --> 00:09:28,226
(Will we starve to death)

183
00:09:28,626 --> 00:09:30,556
if the adults don't come back?

184
00:09:30,986 --> 00:09:32,676
We won't. Look.

185
00:09:32,676 --> 00:09:34,466
My house has a rice cooker.

186
00:09:34,466 --> 00:09:35,156
We won't starve to death

187
00:09:35,156 --> 00:09:37,316
with a rice cooker.

188
00:09:46,536 --> 00:09:47,616
(I once thought)

189
00:09:48,256 --> 00:09:50,656
(that the six of us would be like
the old city we resided in.)

190
00:09:51,416 --> 00:09:52,416
(I thought we would be there)

191
00:09:52,936 --> 00:09:56,336
(for each other forever.)

192
00:10:07,686 --> 00:10:08,326
(However,)

193
00:10:09,046 --> 00:10:10,486
(time changed us)

194
00:10:11,046 --> 00:10:13,006
(and the world.)

195
00:10:31,856 --> 00:10:32,656
Mr. Hao Ping,

196
00:10:33,096 --> 00:10:34,496
I brought the goods you asked for.

197
00:10:35,976 --> 00:10:37,616
Pay me, and you'll receive them.

198
00:10:38,256 --> 00:10:39,736
I'll tell you the keyword

199
00:10:39,736 --> 00:10:40,656
once you transfer the money.

200
00:10:42,096 --> 00:10:43,056
You'll see the content

201
00:10:43,376 --> 00:10:44,176
once you search the keyword.

202
00:10:46,136 --> 00:10:47,056
How should I know

203
00:10:47,776 --> 00:10:49,176
how much it's worth
when you don't have a picture of it?

204
00:10:50,496 --> 00:10:52,776
Didn't we send some pictures to you
before this?

205
00:10:53,096 --> 00:10:53,776
You mean those three pictures?

206
00:10:55,096 --> 00:10:57,336
The pictures weren't even well-defined.

207
00:10:57,336 --> 00:10:58,496
I know paparazzi like you all

208
00:10:58,816 --> 00:10:59,896
too well.

209
00:11:00,656 --> 00:11:02,856
You think you can scare me
with just a few pictures, huh?

210
00:11:03,576 --> 00:11:04,176
Girl,

211
00:11:04,816 --> 00:11:05,776
you're too naive.

212
00:11:06,296 --> 00:11:07,136
Those pictures

213
00:11:07,936 --> 00:11:09,176
are on the house.

214
00:11:12,496 --> 00:11:14,376
15th November, 9:15 PM,

215
00:11:14,376 --> 00:11:15,896
you were wearing a black shirt.

216
00:11:16,256 --> 00:11:17,616
You were meeting the lady in the picture

217
00:11:17,616 --> 00:11:18,976
at Jiangzhou Park.

218
00:11:19,296 --> 00:11:20,616
Her name is Su Jing.

219
00:11:20,616 --> 00:11:21,376
She's 52.

220
00:11:21,696 --> 00:11:22,656
She's a victim of the earthquake.

221
00:11:23,176 --> 00:11:24,976
She received the aid
of your charity fund.

222
00:11:24,976 --> 00:11:26,296
However, she didn't receive the money
after a long time.

223
00:11:26,736 --> 00:11:28,656
Therefore, she contacted the media
and tried to expose you all.

224
00:11:29,456 --> 00:11:30,056
You went there

225
00:11:31,056 --> 00:11:32,936
to buy her silence.

226
00:11:33,576 --> 00:11:34,696
Mind your words.

227
00:11:35,376 --> 00:11:35,876
It's

228
00:11:36,416 --> 00:11:37,296
condolence money.

229
00:11:37,896 --> 00:11:39,376
I didn't buy her silence.

230
00:11:40,896 --> 00:11:42,136
Sorry about this, Mr. Hao Ping.

231
00:11:43,296 --> 00:11:44,176
I came here today

232
00:11:44,616 --> 00:11:46,336
so that you could buy my silence.

233
00:12:03,456 --> 00:12:05,336
Yingzi, the chief editor
is looking for you.

234
00:12:06,336 --> 00:12:07,056
Okay, got it.

235
00:12:10,016 --> 00:12:11,136
Chief Editor, were you looking for me?

236
00:12:11,976 --> 00:12:12,616
Have a seat.

237
00:12:18,216 --> 00:12:19,616
Have you obtained the thing you desired?

238
00:12:20,816 --> 00:12:21,336
Yes.

239
00:12:21,896 --> 00:12:22,936
I can organize

240
00:12:22,936 --> 00:12:24,256
the recordings for you immediately.

241
00:12:24,816 --> 00:12:26,656
However, I hope you can try your best
to protect the victim

242
00:12:26,656 --> 00:12:28,656
with the level of exposure.

243
00:12:29,376 --> 00:12:30,856
You're pretty considerate, huh?

244
00:12:30,856 --> 00:12:31,616
What's next?

245
00:12:34,296 --> 00:12:35,336
You don't know, huh?

246
00:12:36,296 --> 00:12:37,216
I'll tell you, then.

247
00:12:38,856 --> 00:12:40,656
Once this document is published,

248
00:12:41,376 --> 00:12:42,136
you might receive

249
00:12:42,136 --> 00:12:43,496
Hao Ping's lawyer letter tomorrow

250
00:12:43,496 --> 00:12:45,696
for conducting an illegal interview.

251
00:12:45,696 --> 00:12:47,016
But I found the truth.

252
00:12:47,336 --> 00:12:48,216
This truth

253
00:12:48,536 --> 00:12:49,456
will show the people

254
00:12:49,456 --> 00:12:50,456
the true colors of a sanctimonious

255
00:12:50,456 --> 00:12:52,096
elite investor.

256
00:12:52,416 --> 00:12:54,296
We can prevent more people
from getting cheated.

257
00:12:54,656 --> 00:12:55,576
Isn't that

258
00:12:55,696 --> 00:12:56,616
the most important part?

259
00:12:57,856 --> 00:12:59,096
Why must you guys

260
00:12:59,496 --> 00:13:01,576
live like parasites?

261
00:13:02,976 --> 00:13:03,976
You guys are so greedy,

262
00:13:04,336 --> 00:13:06,256
making ridiculous demands
when there's a chance.

263
00:13:06,376 --> 00:13:07,336
When I give you more,

264
00:13:07,456 --> 00:13:08,136
you want more.

265
00:13:08,816 --> 00:13:10,416
But you can't just say that.

266
00:13:10,976 --> 00:13:11,856
After all, you were the one

267
00:13:12,056 --> 00:13:13,736
who tried to "help" them
in the first place.

268
00:13:14,256 --> 00:13:16,416
In the end, you used charity
as an excuse

269
00:13:16,416 --> 00:13:17,776
to put the money you collected

270
00:13:17,776 --> 00:13:19,576
into your own pockets.

271
00:13:19,576 --> 00:13:20,576
How did you trick

272
00:13:20,576 --> 00:13:22,176
all those who donated money?

273
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:24,136
I didn't trick them.

274
00:13:24,456 --> 00:13:25,096
I just

275
00:13:25,736 --> 00:13:28,136
gave them a reasonable pathway

276
00:13:28,136 --> 00:13:30,776
to satisfy their overflowing sympathy.

277
00:13:32,576 --> 00:13:33,896
In this world,

278
00:13:34,456 --> 00:13:36,936
you can solve everything with money.

